quran[4]{c,v,t}:
  2,58,"Ciftoree e neemaaji Alla dow mon,nde Min mbii on:naatee ndee saare (Baytil Mukaddas),Гұaamee toon belЙ—i ceniiЙ—i e kala nokku Й—o mbela-Й—on, so oЙ—on naata damal ngal tugganon Alla tiiЙ—e,toro-Й—on Alla mbi'on: Joomi amen momtan min bakkatuuji amen;Min njaЙ“ana on,maa Min Й“eydan moЖҙЖҙinЙ“e golle maЙ“Й“e Й“ee baraaji."
  2,59,"ЖҒeen tooГұЙ“e mbattiti konngol tanaa ngol Й“e mbi'anoo, Й“e naatiri ladgol, Й“e mbi*i: gabbel nder leebol sabu jalkitde yamiroore Alla toowЙ—o O; njoЙ“di tooГұooЙ“e Й“e ko Alla njippini dow maЙ“Й“e lette sabu yaltugol maЙ“Й“e keerol sariya e luutndaade yamiroore."
  2,60,"Ciftoree moЖҙЖҙi Alla dow mon nde majju-Й—on nde, wemmbere bonnde heЙ“i on, ndeen Muusaa (jkm) toranii on Joomiraawo O yarna on; Min njamiri mo fiyirde haayre nde sawru makko; nde o fiynoo nde tan gite ndiyam sappo e Й—iЙ—i puccitii tolnondir e limoore leГұГұi mon Й—i, ndiyam suppitii heen, Min mbii on: Гұaamee njaron e njeЙ—u ngu Alla addani on te on tampanaani Й—um, taa mbaЙ—ee bonannde e leydi hee."
  2,61,"Ciftoree nde njeddu-Й—on moЖҙЖҙere Jooma mon,kaaЙ“-Й—on mbii-Й—on Muusaa:min muГұataa e Гұaamdu wooturu,torano amen Jooma maa O yaltinana min Гұaandu iwde e puЙ—i lesdi,gila e haako e kecciЙ—Й—i mayri haa e buudi e gabbe e Гұebbe e basalle mayri;Muusaa (jkm) wii e waasde weleede Й—aЙ“Й“al mon: on mbattitat ko Й“uri jaasde Й—um ko okka-Й—on,oЙ—on keЙ“annoo Й—um ko aldaa e tampere-: njippee e ndi leydi faade e wooto e gure Й—e, maa on taw toon ko toriЙ—on ko,nde Й“e ndewi belaaЙ—e maЙ“Й“e Й“e calii ko Alla suЙ“anii Й“e,Й“e keddodi e hoyre e baasal e Й“ittere,Й“e nduttii e tikkire Alla; sabu salaade Й“e diine Makko,e yeddu- de Й“e aayeeji Makko,e tooГұe ko Й“e mbannoo annabaaЙ“e Makko, Й—uum fof addi Й—um ko woopde Й“e Alla e ko Й“e njawtatno keeri Makko."